(power_pad, time).explanation: Power pad design and placement directly affects I/O timing characteristics and signal propagation delays in processor circuits;

(power_pad, area_net_area).explanation: Power pad placement and configuration directly influences the routing area required for interconnect nets between I/O pads and internal logic;

(power_pad, area_cell_area).explanation: Power pads and logic cell area are independent design components that do not directly influence each other's physical area requirements;
